data.description: Take a look at this investment opportunity! Great Northside Neighborhood. Open Floor Plan with vaulted ceilings and a Large Living Room. Full Dining Room and a Nice Size Rear Kitchen. Lots of Cabinets and Counter Space, a Breakfast Bar and Pantry. Primary Bedroom has access to the Rear Covered Patio and a walk-in closet. Lots of possibilities with this property! Great Floor Plan, Open & Spacious.  Good Yard Size, Side Parking with Hook Ups! You can Make this Home Your Own! Spa sized wading Pool is sold in as-is condition, sellers have no knowledge of the last time it was operational.
